title: First Dates couple stunned as they realise they already know each other for incredible reason
text:
First Dates couple stunned as they realise they already know each other for incredible reason Vince and Anna couldn't believe they'd been paired up 20 years after their first date! Share this video Get celebs   Thank you for subscribing!   
First Dates saw a HILARIOUS coincidence on tonight’s episode, as a couple realised they’d already been on a date 20 years before! 
Vince and Anna, both from Manchester, were introduced on the Channel 4 show, but it took a shocking turn when they realised they’d already met. 
Immediately, Anna said she recognised Vince, and she said: “I’m sure you know my cousin.” 
When he said he did, she added: “I think you know me too!” Anna was shocked when she recognised Vince (Photo: Channel 4) Vince couldn't believe it! (Photo: Channel 4) 
And Vince suddenly realised: “We’ve been on a date!” 
Vince had even been to Anna’s house all those years ago - and they’d kissed! 
Speaking about why it never went anywhere, Vince said: “I liked you, I remember that much. I think there might have been another guy in the background.” Read More They'd already been on a date! (Photo: Channel 4) Unbelieveable! (Photo: Channel 4) 
And then, speaking to camera, he said: “I fancied her all those years ago and I still do now.” 
Vince and Anna both decided to see each other again, and she added: “We need to find out what happened!” 
*First Dates continues on Channel 4 on Monday at 9pm Like us on Facebook
